metadata.name: 01 : Toko Kelontong
metadata.description:
a phenomenon that often occurs in Indonesia. where people are just trying to try their luck or trying to survive by opening a shop that sells a variety of goods and food. 
a random shop that I think is a bit strange. 
but sometimes they have items that are difficult to find in specific stores/super markets and sometimes they sell something with dubious or even expired packaging.
